    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine Domini Dei Salvatoris nostri Iesu Christi. Nos <rs
                            key="#Vir_gloriosus/vir_sublimis">vir gloriosissimus</rs>
                        <persName key="#Princeps" ref="#people/186">Sicardus</persName>Dei
                        previdentia gentis Langubardorum <rs key="#Princeps">princeps</rs>, motus
                        Dei omnipotentis misericordia et pro redemptione anime nostre seu gentis et
                        patrie, suggerente potestati nostre <rs key="#Personal_rank">viro
                            venerabile</rs>
                        <persName key="#Prevosts" ref="#people/192">Bassaci</persName>
                        <rs key="#Prevosts">preposito</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Landed_possessions #Monasteries" ref="#juridical_persons/85"
                                ><rs key="#Monasteries">monasterio</rs> Sancte Sophie</orgName> sito
                        infra hanc Beneventanam nostram civitatem <rs key="#Intercessory">per</rs>
                        <persName key="#Intercessory #Other_palatine_officer" ref="#people/3463"
                            >Radelgis</persName>
                        <rs key="#Other_palatine_officer">thesaurarium</rs> nostrum, concedimus in
                        prephato Beate Sophie monasterio, ubi <persName key="#Abbesses"
                            ref="#people/3461">Wilerona</persName>
                        <rs key="#Abbesses">abbatissa</rs> preesse videtur, <rs
                            key="#Fisheries #Fish #Fiscal_property #Object #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >piscariam</rs> sacri nostri palatii que dicitur Flumen Longum in
                        integrum, et ab ipso flumine infra <placeName key="#Lakes #Fiscal_property"
                            ref="#places/3460">pantanum</placeName> signa ita posita <rs key="#Size"
                            >in longitudine miliarium unum et in latitudine passus ducenti</rs> erga
                        ipsum <rs key="#Rivers">fluvium</rs> et infra <rs
                            key="#Lakes #Marshes/lagoons/tombolos"><placeName ref="#places/554"
                                key="#Lakes #Marshes/lagoons/tombolos">pantanum</placeName></rs> cum
                            <rs key="#Shores">ripis</rs> et <rs key="#Roads">viis</rs> suis, et in
                        terra firma<rs key="#Size"> terra modiorum quinquaginta</rs> ubi <rs
                            key="#Houses">habitatio</rs> de ipsis <rs key="#Specialized_workers"
                            >piscatoribus</rs> sit, <rs
                            key="#Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters">et pascuum in ipsa insula
                            ad peculia illorum qui ibi residunt, et de ipso pantano cannas et paleas
                            tollendum quantum opus fuerit, et ligna de ipsa insula tollendum quantum
                            opus fuerit ad eorum utilitatem</rs> in ipso loco peragendam. Hec omnia
                        supra dicta pertinuerunt de <rs key="#Actio">actu <placeName
                                key="#Cities #Fiscal_property" ref="#places/2349"
                                >Lucerino</placeName></rs>, <rs key="#Iudiciaria">iudiciaria</rs>
                        <persName ref="#people/3464" key="#Gastaldus/vicegastaldus"
                            >Aczoni</persName>
                        <rs key="#Gastaldus/vicegastaldus">gastaldi</rs> nostri. Et concessimus in
                        eodem monasterio <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions #Fiscal_property #Object #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >terra</rs> in finibus <placeName
                            key="#Geographic_regions #Fiscal_property" ref="#places/3410"
                            >Apuleę</placeName> in territorio Virisiano propinquo <orgName
                            key="#Churches" ref="#juridical_persons/3437"><rs key="#Churches"
                                >ęcclesia</rs> Sancti Decorentii</orgName>
                        <rs key="#Size">modio trecenti</rs>, que fuit de quodam <name
                            ref="Garetruda">Garetruda</name> relicta Wiconis gastaldi cum <rs
                            key="#Houses">casa</rs> que ibidem edificata est et cum superioribus et
                        inferioribus suis in integrum qualiter secundum legem <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Mention #Inflow">ad sacrum nostrum palatium
                            evenit</rs>, que pertinuit de <rs key="#Iudiciaria">iudiciaria</rs>
                        supra dicti Radelgis, in ea videlicet ratione ut amodo et deinceps per hoc
                        nostrum roboreum preceptum cuncta que preleguntur ipsum monasterium et eius
                        rectores securo nomine habere et possidere et perfrui valeant et a nullis ex
                        nostris iudicibus, id est comitibus, gastaldis, vel a quibuscumque agentibus
                        habeant aliquam requisitionem rectores prephati monasterii, sed perpetuis
                        temporibus ea que nunc concessimus ibidem securiter possideantur. Quod vero
                            <rs key="#Marquis’/ducal/princely_diploma">preceptum concessionis</rs>
                        ex iussione nominate potestatis scripsi ego <persName key="#Notary"
                            ref="#people/3465">Audoaldus</persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs>. Actus <placeName key="#Cities"
                            ref="#places/110">Beneventus</placeName> in sacro <rs key="#Palatium"
                            >palatio</rs> tertio anno, mense martio, tertia decima indictione.
                        Feliciter.</ab>
                </div>
